"""Multi-asset deep learning feature engineering.

Generates, validates, and ranks DL features for 3 assets:
  - BTC  (from local sim_1m.sqlite, 4h timeframe)
  - NVDA (from yfinance, daily)
  - AMZN (from yfinance, daily)

