    get_btc_features(db_path, timeframe="4h") -> (X, y, feature_names)
    get_nvda_features() -> (X, y, feature_names)
    get_amzn_features() -> (X, y, feature_names)

Usage:
    py -3.12 scripts/dl_features.py
